						<summary>

						<p>States that <hi rend="bold">Vishṇu (?)</hi> the minister of <hi rend="bold">Vīrabhadrēśvara</hi> of the <hi rend="bold">Chālukya</hi>-<hi rend="italic">vaṁśa</hi> who married <hi rend="bold">Kākatīya Gaṇapatidēva's</hi> daughter <hi rend="bold">Rudrama-Mahādēvi</hi> presented a perpetual lamp to the temple of Sōmēśvara of <hi rend="bold">Ḍuttika.</hi> The inscription is incomplete.</p>						

						</summary>
